{"tid":1820541,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人勿對台仔有恩主心態","createTime":"2020-01-11T14:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T00:13:52.000Z","uid":77532,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46e23a83f41904599705e8ea9a122d3bf836108c","tid":1820541,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"香港人抗爭唔係換取蔡英文選票<br />\n抗爭係為咗香港民主<br />\n的確可能提升咗台灣本土意識<br />\n但係票係佢地嘅<br />\n正如自由行雖然幫到一部份香港經濟<br />\n但係佢哋玩得開心<br />\n香港人辛勤工作先有今日嘅經濟成就<br />\n不斷消費呢件事嘅恩客心態係香港人討厭支那人五毛主因之一<br />\n<br />\n對中國對敵人<br />\n強調當年對中國嘅投資同埋幫助<br />\n宣傳又好 同仇敵愾又好 冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n對民主同路人<br />\n唔好變成自己最討厭嘅人<br />\n（功利主義：保持友善先啦，係要辣着咗多個火頭 <br />\n從政係想唔支持你嘅人支持你呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f24f36064bbba3278c0bb576bc9ac52f23f22d","tid":1820541,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4340b49573fa65a9f02be6a839eddda9739cf62b","tid":1820541,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4887a65840828587a77b9d0aace4d20fe8278877","tid":1820541,"uid":7990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a074c6b0a45158a4af5094dfb1d0df4124d7c03a","tid":1820541,"uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"唔好成為自己討厭的人，記住呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZBEAbvSUJjc/UPUM62BXSvI/AAAAAAAAJTc/U-R8kedr_0I/s1600/up289092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZBEAbvSUJjc%2FUPUM62BXSvI%2FAAAAAAAAJTc%2FU-R8kedr_0I%2Fs1600%2Fup289092.jpg&h=533eef8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74b8b563716f65d2d2ed586c9979810fe1ad26ad","tid":1820541,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820242</a>"},{"pid":"b4dcea065dc49f9f2c86a3806d0c08904860c978","tid":1820541,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"你啱嘅<br />\n事實係蔡英文執死雞<br />\n如果唔係比人滲透得太勁其實兩黨輪替係好事<br />\n依家最大得益者係民進黨<br />\n唔係台灣人"},{"pid":"9ff633bdc4b78c1220f67c7b757e2317776a42df","tid":1820541,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"yup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCheng Lap:蔡英文當選之後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820271</a>"},{"pid":"9cd4e1f51bea9ca786583e25650f14b25160fd94","tid":1820541,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff633bdc4b78c1220f67c7b757e2317776a42df","tid":1820541,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"yup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCheng Lap:蔡英文當選之後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820271</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"好啦 其實我政治啟蒙係鄭立"},{"pid":"b9ee3b367bb7b3969df92ca4811e2db4141e3dea","tid":1820541,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd4e1f51bea9ca786583e25650f14b25160fd94","tid":1820541,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff633bdc4b78c1220f67c7b757e2317776a42df","tid":1820541,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"yup<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor